rong>Investor:</strong> I=E2=80=99ll take $50 million.</p><p style=3D"margi=
n: 16px 0;"><strong>Josh A.:</strong> Oh wow it says here CDN stands for =
=E2=80=9Ccontent delivery network.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"mar=
